### Pricing Enhanced Items

Calculate costs by multiplying the base item cost by the enhancement multiplier:

**+1 Longsword:** 40 coins (longsword) × 10 (+1 multiplier) = 400 coins
**+2 Chainmail:** 75 coins (chainmail) × 50 (+2 multiplier) = 3,750 coins
**+3 Greatsword:** 50 coins (greatsword) × 200 (+3 multiplier) = 10,000 coins

These prices assume magic items can be purchased. Many campaigns treat magic items as treasure-only, making monetary cost irrelevant.

